data.description: Large 4 Bedroom dual master home in convenient Sangaree. New carpet, new luxury vinyl plank in the down stairs master. Bamboo flooring in main living areas and a beamed ceiling. Paint has been refreshed. The large backyard features a firepit and is surrounded by a beautifully constructed wooden privacy fence.
